column5: Anyone have any reports on Warwick lake, north of red lake this year???

Not a report as such but I was there briefly on 6/26; we had a 3 man group that stopped there to pick up a couple guys that they couldn't fit on the plane (large group) - they told us they did real well - they were primarily after walleye. Sorry but that's all I've got.
Thanks for info. Will be heading up in a few weeks
